    "asOf": "2022-04-05",
    "date": "2022-04-11T13:59:13Z",
    "text": "Educators Expense Deduction Modernization Act of 2022\n\nThis bill increases the tax deduction for the expenses of eligible educators from $250 to $1,000, An eligible educator is, with respect to any taxable year, an individual who is a kindergarten through grade 12 teacher, instructor, counselor, principal, or aide in a school for at least 900 hours during a school year."
